So here I share with you 4 different ways to use a black dress: first look is sporty, second look is casual for events during the day, third for a date and fourth to go to an event or conference. Hope you like them! xx 
Hola amigos,💖
Aquí les comparto 4 looks diferentes para usar un vestido negro: el primer look deportivo, para salir a pasear casual, el tercero para una cita, cuarto para un evento o conferencia. Espero les guste! xx

Song: Ben Woodward - Singing in the Rain
Link: https://youtu.be/30W8UFSZ8bs
Music promoted by FreeMusicWave.

node.text:
How are you almost 9 months, my angel? 💕🥺 found this beautiful quote recently and fell in love: 

“Hold her a little longer, rock her a little more, read her another story, you’ve only read her four. Let her sleep on your shoulder, rejoice in her happy smile. She is only a little girl for such a little while.” 🌸
————
Cómo es posible que ya casi tienes 9 meses mi ángel? Wow! 🥺🙏🏽💕 encontré esta cita recientemente que me encantó: 

“Abrázala por mas tiempo, mécela un poco más, léele otra historia, solo le has leído cuatro. Déjala dormir en tu hombro, regocíjate con su sonrisa feliz. Ella es solo una niña por tan poco tiempo”. 🌸🙏🏽
